1
00:00:01,129 --> 00:00:03,299
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

2
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:10,470
<Default><b>Another rigged
match, huh?</b></Default>

3
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:12,560
<Default><b>I'm just happy
you're back.</b></Default>

4
00:00:14,259 --> 00:00:15,339
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

5
00:00:19,809 --> 00:00:20,889
<Default><b>[clinks]</b></Default>

6
00:00:21,769 --> 00:00:23,209
<Default><b>[gate slams shut]</b></Default>

7
00:00:23,649 --> 00:00:24,969
<Default><b>[keys turning]</b></Default>

8
00:00:26,690 --> 00:00:28,699
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

9
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:36,515
<Default><b>Hey there, Atla</b></Default>

10
00:00:36,539 --> 00:00:37,659
<Default><b>I'm back.</b></Default>

11
00:00:38,460 --> 00:00:39,460
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

12
00:00:40,329 --> 00:00:43,000
<Default><b>I'm glad that
you're back</b></Default>

13
00:00:43,960 --> 00:00:46,590
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

14
00:00:54,390 --> 00:00:56,679
<Default><b>Here.
Have something to eat.</b></Default>

15
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:09,780
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

16
00:01:09,950 --> 00:01:10,990
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

17
00:01:11,739 --> 00:01:12,739
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

18
00:01:18,909 --> 00:01:20,500
<Default><b>[breathing]</b></Default>

19
00:01:21,790 --> 00:01:22,805
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

20
00:01:22,829 --> 00:01:25,340
<Default><b>[FALSE SLAVE
03-A (F)] Aww</b></Default>

21
00:01:26,090 --> 00:01:28,275
<Default><b>[FALSE SLAVE 03-B (F)] Only
until the Shield Hero buys us</b></Default>

22
00:01:28,299 --> 00:01:30,019
<Default><b>then we'll be home free.</b></Default>

23
00:01:30,469 --> 00:01:31,986
<Default><b>[sighs]
I just hope he comes</b></Default>

24
00:01:32,010 --> 00:01:33,490
<Default><b>sooner than later.</b></Default>

25
00:01:34,390 --> 00:01:36,150
<Default><b>The Shield
Hero's coming?</b></Default>

26
00:03:21,699 --> 00:03:24,539
<Default><b>Please! Won't
you help us</b></Default>

27
00:03:24,789 --> 00:03:27,169
<Default><b>You're here to save us</b></Default>

28
00:03:27,250 --> 00:03:29,605
<Default><b>You'll buy me
and get me out of here, right?</b></Default>

29
00:03:29,629 --> 00:03:30,500
<Default><b>I beg of you.</b></Default>

30
00:03:30,590 --> 00:03:32,645
<Default><b>Don't let me die
in a horrible place like this.</b></Default>

31
00:03:32,669 --> 00:03:35,276
<Default><b>You're not fooling anyone
with an act like that.</b></Default>

32
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:36,340
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

33
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:37,719
<Default><b>Hm...</b></Default>

34
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,930
<Default><b>You're a keen
one, Shield Hero!</b></Default>

35
00:03:41,009 --> 00:03:42,906
<Default><b>You identified those
fake slaves</b></Default>

36
00:03:42,930 --> 00:03:44,195
<Default><b>without any hesitation!</b></Default>

37
00:03:44,219 --> 00:03:46,165
<Default><b>It's almost enough
to make me shiver.</b></Default>

38
00:03:46,189 --> 00:03:47,789
<Default><b>What's going on here?</b></Default>

39
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:50,650
<Default><b>In Siltvelt</b></Default>

40
00:03:50,729 --> 00:03:54,110
<Default><b>and really, who wouldn't
want to be bought up by a God!</b></Default>

41
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,949
<Default><b>Now, what do you say
we get down to business?</b></Default>

42
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:59,699
<Default><b>The main attraction
is just this way.</b></Default>

43
00:04:00,569 --> 00:04:02,080
<Default><b>- Huh...
- [grunts]</b></Default>

44
00:04:02,740 --> 00:04:05,080
<Default><b>Darn it! I only came
to this stink hole</b></Default>

45
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:06,635
<Default><b>because Daddy made me!</b></Default>

46
00:04:06,659 --> 00:04:09,299
<Default><b>[FALSE SLAVE 03-B (F)]
[sighs] He's so handsome.</b></Default>

47
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:12,289
<Default><b>Shield Hero, please!
Over here!</b></Default>

48
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:15,840
<Default><b>Please sir.
Please buy the both of us!</b></Default>

49
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:17,879
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

50
00:04:18,470 --> 00:04:20,150
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I've seen you.</b></Default>

51
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:23,310
<Default><b>Tell me, what's
your name?</b></Default>

52
00:04:23,389 --> 00:04:24,749
<Default><b>My name's Fohl.</b></Default>

53
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,165
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
What makes this one special</b></Default>

54
00:04:28,189 --> 00:04:30,480
<Default><b>is his sought after
combat ability.</b></Default>

55
00:04:30,810 --> 00:04:33,319
<Default><b>If you don't believe me</b></Default>

56
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:37,950
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] His level is this
high at such a young age?</b></Default>

57
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:40,819
<Default><b>White tigers are
unlike any other race.</b></Default>

58
00:04:40,910 --> 00:04:43,490
<Default><b>They can upgrade their
class up to level 60</b></Default>

59
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:44,636
<Default><b>and after that</b></Default>

60
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:47,079
<Default><b>they can
reach level 120!</b></Default>

61
00:04:47,209 --> 00:04:49,129
<Default><b>And having a
higher max level</b></Default>

62
00:04:49,170 --> 00:04:50,555
<Default><b>means higher stats.</b></Default>

63
00:04:50,579 --> 00:04:53,019
<Default><b>Will he get even stronger
when he grows up?</b></Default>

64
00:04:53,129 --> 00:04:55,250
<Default><b>Yes.
Not counting the heroes</b></Default>

65
00:04:55,339 --> 00:04:58,179
<Default><b>they are among the most
powerful beings in the world!</b></Default>

66
00:04:58,470 --> 00:05:01,970
<Default><b>He could be yours
for just 120 gold pieces.</b></Default>

67
00:05:02,139 --> 00:05:03,179
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

68
00:05:03,889 --> 00:05:05,249
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

69
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,919
<Default><b>I understand that
he could be valuable.</b></Default>

70
00:05:08,389 --> 00:05:10,509
<Default><b>You said there's
two of you though?</b></Default>

71
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,480
<Default><b>Yes, I have
a little sister.</b></Default>

72
00:05:12,899 --> 00:05:15,189
<Default><b>If you buy me</b></Default>

73
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:17,649
<Default><b>It's true that
they're siblings</b></Default>

74
00:05:17,730 --> 00:05:19,125
<Default><b>but the sister is blind</b></Default>

75
00:05:19,149 --> 00:05:21,509
<Default><b>and too sickly to
even rise from her bed.</b></Default>

76
00:05:21,949 --> 00:05:24,660
<Default><b>I'd have a hard time
getting 30 silvers for her!</b></Default>

77
00:05:25,370 --> 00:05:26,730
<Default><b>That poor girl.</b></Default>

78
00:05:26,870 --> 00:05:29,096
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
Because his sister is so feeble</b></Default>

79
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:31,370
<Default><b>he fights in the
underground coliseum</b></Default>

80
00:05:31,459 --> 00:05:33,500
<Default><b>to pay for her
food and medicine.</b></Default>

81
00:05:33,579 --> 00:05:36,589
<Default><b>Ah. It's enough to bring
a tear to my eye.</b></Default>

82
00:05:37,050 --> 00:05:39,130
<Default><b>I don't believe that
for a second.</b></Default>

83
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:41,700
<Default><b>I'm sure you take
a big cut of his earnings.</b></Default>

84
00:05:41,930 --> 00:05:43,526
<Default><b>Haha! There you go again</b></Default>

85
00:05:43,550 --> 00:05:45,615
<Default><b>surprising me with
just how keen you are</b></Default>

86
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:47,359
<Default><b>- Shield Hero!
- Scumbag!</b></Default>

87
00:05:48,220 --> 00:05:50,326
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What's your sister's name?</b></Default>

88
00:05:50,350 --> 00:05:51,639
<Default><b>It's Atla.</b></Default>

89
00:05:52,389 --> 00:05:54,060
<Default><b>- Open the cell.
- Huh?</b></Default>

90
00:05:54,269 --> 00:05:55,589
<Default><b>[keys turning]</b></Default>

91
00:05:58,529 --> 00:06:00,129
<Default><b>- Hm?
- [gate closing]</b></Default>

92
00:06:03,949 --> 00:06:05,569
<Default><b>Who are you?</b></Default>

93
00:06:06,279 --> 00:06:09,040
<Default><b>Naofumi Iwatani.
The Shield Hero.</b></Default>

94
00:06:09,490 --> 00:06:11,870
<Default><b>Thank you for coming</b></Default>

95
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,420
<Default><b>All I ask is that</b></Default>

96
00:06:13,620 --> 00:06:16,040
<Default><b>you take my brother
far away from here.</b></Default>

97
00:06:16,379 --> 00:06:17,685
<Default><b>- I don't have...
- Sorry</b></Default>

98
00:06:17,709 --> 00:06:20,509
<Default><b>but I'm not about to
leave you in a place like this.</b></Default>

99
00:06:27,930 --> 00:06:29,170
<Default><b>What's that?</b></Default>

100
00:06:29,350 --> 00:06:30,536
<Default><b>Wait, could it be?</b></Default>

101
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,769
<Default><b>An Elixir of Yggdrasil.</b></Default>

102
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:35,100
<Default><b>If I give this
to your sister</b></Default>

103
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,495
<Default><b>are you ready to spend</b></Default>

104
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:38,679
<Default><b>the rest of your
life paying for it?</b></Default>

105
00:06:39,649 --> 00:06:41,439
<Default><b>Yes</b></Default>

106
00:06:41,689 --> 00:06:42,966
<Default><b>To pay for her</b></Default>

107
00:06:42,990 --> 00:06:45,030
<Default><b>and four more others
if you want!</b></Default>

108
00:06:45,110 --> 00:06:46,270
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

109
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,040
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

110
00:07:00,050 --> 00:07:01,050
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

111
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:07,089
<Default><b>I feel so warm.</b></Default>

112
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:09,220
<Default><b>The pain is gone.</b></Default>

113
00:07:10,509 --> 00:07:11,549
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

114
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:13,639
<Default><b>Atla.</b></Default>

115
00:07:13,889 --> 00:07:15,249
<Default><b>It's a miracle.</b></Default>

116
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,920
<Default><b>I was so worried!</b></Default>

117
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:18,586
<Default><b>For it to fully work</b></Default>

118
00:07:18,610 --> 00:07:21,530
<Default><b>she'll need to take more
doses of the elixir over time.</b></Default>

119
00:07:21,730 --> 00:07:23,570
<Default><b>But for now,
get some rest.</b></Default>

120
00:07:23,990 --> 00:07:26,529
<Default><b>Right.
Thank you for your kindness.</b></Default>

121
00:07:26,910 --> 00:07:27,910
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

122
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:32,740
<Default><b>Raphtalia</b></Default>

123
00:07:32,949 --> 00:07:33,989
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

124
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:35,750
<Default><b>Right!</b></Default>

125
00:07:38,170 --> 00:07:40,570
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] After we purchased
Fohl and Atla</b></Default>

126
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:42,855
<Default><b>we met with Sadeena
and the other slaves</b></Default>

127
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:44,026
<Default><b>from Lurolona Village</b></Default>

128
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:46,156
<Default><b>who we took back
from the coliseum.</b></Default>

129
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:48,389
<Default><b>We then headed
back to our village.</b></Default>

130
00:07:48,509 --> 00:07:50,350
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

131
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,590
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

132
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,970
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

133
00:07:58,980 --> 00:08:00,560
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

134
00:08:05,610 --> 00:08:07,090
<Default><b>Big sister Sadeena</b></Default>

135
00:08:07,149 --> 00:08:09,199
<Default><b>can we be together</b></Default>

136
00:08:09,490 --> 00:08:10,910
<Default><b>Yes, we can!</b></Default>

137
00:08:10,990 --> 00:08:12,750
<Default><b>- Because now...
- [gasps]</b></Default>

138
00:08:12,779 --> 00:08:14,805
<Default><b>...I'm in love with
Naofumi Iwatani</b></Default>

139
00:08:14,829 --> 00:08:16,229
<Default><b>the Shield Hero!</b></Default>

140
00:08:16,329 --> 00:08:17,935
<Default><b>What are you
doing, Sadeena?</b></Default>

141
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:18,976
<Default><b>Don't tell me</b></Default>

142
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,396
<Default><b>you didn't end
up getting yourself</b></Default>

143
00:08:20,420 --> 00:08:22,565
<Default><b>into a drinking contest
with her, did you?</b></Default>

144
00:08:22,589 --> 00:08:23,646
<Default><b>No, I didn't!</b></Default>

145
00:08:23,670 --> 00:08:25,396
<Default><b>It was one
drink, that's all.</b></Default>

146
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:27,550
<Default><b>Oh. Seeing you
all grown up now</b></Default>

147
00:08:27,629 --> 00:08:30,389
<Default><b>really brings a
tear to my eye, Raphtalia!</b></Default>

148
00:08:31,050 --> 00:08:32,799
<Default><b>[thumping]</b></Default>

149
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,640
<Default><b>[thump]</b></Default>

150
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:36,719
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

151
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:41,380
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Our population
is growing nicely</b></Default>

152
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:43,520
<Default><b>but our defenses
still need work.</b></Default>

153
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,706
<Default><b>We have to
fix that soon.</b></Default>

154
00:08:45,730 --> 00:08:47,890
<Default><b>If we want to
keep our village safe.</b></Default>

155
00:08:48,110 --> 00:08:52,120
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

156
00:08:53,330 --> 00:08:54,530
<Default><b>As for Atla</b></Default>

157
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:57,580
<Default><b>she got a little better
with each drink of the elixir.</b></Default>

158
00:08:59,169 --> 00:09:00,209
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

159
00:09:01,379 --> 00:09:03,355
<Default><b>We're going to have
to start getting serious</b></Default>

160
00:09:03,379 --> 00:09:05,899
<Default><b>about selling these
Bio Plants and medicines.</b></Default>

161
00:09:06,299 --> 00:09:07,816
<Default><b>We don't have
quite enough money</b></Default>

162
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,840
<Default><b>to build proper
facilities yet.</b></Default>

163
00:09:10,590 --> 00:09:11,889
<Default><b>Hey, Naofumi.</b></Default>

164
00:09:12,049 --> 00:09:14,025
<Default><b>Are you really all right
with taking care of</b></Default>

165
00:09:14,049 --> 00:09:16,326
<Default><b>all these new kids
we have staying here now?</b></Default>

166
00:09:16,350 --> 00:09:17,576
<Default><b>It'll be fine.</b></Default>

167
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,785
<Default><b>We're starting to make more
from trading.</b></Default>

168
00:09:19,809 --> 00:09:22,019
<Default><b>I'm not just talking
about the money.</b></Default>

169
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:25,320
<Default><b>We're basically the parents
of a huge family now.</b></Default>

170
00:09:25,820 --> 00:09:27,490
<Default><b>[MELTY] I mean</b></Default>

171
00:09:27,570 --> 00:09:29,450
<Default><b>to make
everyone breakfast</b></Default>

172
00:09:30,779 --> 00:09:32,255
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
He has, hasn't he?</b></Default>

173
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:33,479
<Default><b>- Hm.
- Huh?</b></Default>

174
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:35,385
<Default><b>The lights have been
on in here</b></Default>

175
00:09:35,409 --> 00:09:37,289
<Default><b>nearly all
night, you two.</b></Default>

176
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:40,096
<Default><b>It's good to have
more friends in the village</b></Default>

177
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,436
<Default><b>but don't work too hard.</b></Default>

178
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:43,580
<Default><b>You'll burn yourself out
if you do.</b></Default>

179
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:45,940
<Default><b>Not to mention...</b></Default>

180
00:09:46,129 --> 00:09:47,129
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

181
00:09:47,169 --> 00:09:48,369
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

182
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,040
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

183
00:09:51,509 --> 00:09:52,509
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

184
00:09:53,679 --> 00:09:55,696
<Default><b>- Are you serious, Sadeena?
- [gasps]</b></Default>

185
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:58,309
<Default><b>Can't you see Master Naofumi
is still working?</b></Default>

186
00:09:58,389 --> 00:10:00,826
<Default><b>We don't need you
bringing alcohol in here!</b></Default>

187
00:10:00,850 --> 00:10:03,440
<Default><b>Aww, it's fine!</b></Default>

188
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:05,809
<Default><b>To me, this
is just water!</b></Default>

189
00:10:05,899 --> 00:10:07,480
<Default><b>That's all. Water!</b></Default>

190
00:10:07,610 --> 00:10:08,755
<Default><b>- [chuckles]
- [groans]</b></Default>

191
00:10:08,779 --> 00:10:10,716
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
The water of life, that is!</b></Default>

192
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:12,200
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

193
00:10:19,580 --> 00:10:21,039
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

194
00:10:21,460 --> 00:10:23,750
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

195
00:10:32,259 --> 00:10:33,299
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

196
00:10:33,470 --> 00:10:35,009
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

197
00:10:40,929 --> 00:10:44,100
<Default><b>I'm glad that you were able to
take the bandages off already.</b></Default>

198
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,875
<Default><b>How do you feel?</b></Default>

199
00:10:45,899 --> 00:10:47,579
<Default><b>It's such a difference.</b></Default>

200
00:10:47,809 --> 00:10:49,289
<Default><b>Thank you so much!</b></Default>

201
00:10:50,070 --> 00:10:53,110
<Default><b>Hey, easy there, Atla</b></Default>

202
00:10:54,029 --> 00:10:55,029
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

203
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,755
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I'm headed off to Lute Village</b></Default>

204
00:10:57,779 --> 00:11:00,499
<Default><b>to discuss trade routes
and conduct some business.</b></Default>

205
00:11:01,789 --> 00:11:03,806
<Default><b>Take a walk to practice
using your legs again</b></Default>

206
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:04,936
<Default><b>all right?</b></Default>

207
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,960
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

208
00:11:07,830 --> 00:11:09,590
<Default><b>Atla, you ready?</b></Default>

209
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,549
<Default><b>Yes, let's be off.</b></Default>

210
00:11:11,799 --> 00:11:13,419
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

211
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:18,389
<Default><b>It smells so nice.</b></Default>

212
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:19,889
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

213
00:11:21,220 --> 00:11:23,809
<Default><b>[FOHL] This feeling.
I've felt it before.</b></Default>

214
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:25,389
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

215
00:11:26,649 --> 00:11:28,169
<Default><b>[ATLA] Big brother.</b></Default>

216
00:11:28,309 --> 00:11:29,399
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

217
00:11:30,019 --> 00:11:31,649
<Default><b>Sorry, what is it?</b></Default>

218
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:34,029
<Default><b>I want to practice
standing up again.</b></Default>

219
00:11:34,279 --> 00:11:35,360
<Default><b>Sure.</b></Default>

220
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:37,340
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- [chuckles]</b></Default>

221
00:11:39,330 --> 00:11:40,990
<Default><b>Okay, ready?</b></Default>

222
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,596
<Default><b>I'm letting go now.</b></Default>

223
00:11:42,620 --> 00:11:43,620
<Default><b>Ready.</b></Default>

224
00:11:48,250 --> 00:11:49,830
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

225
00:11:50,250 --> 00:11:52,250
<Default><b>We're done</b></Default>

226
00:11:53,169 --> 00:11:54,259
<Default><b>Not yet.</b></Default>

227
00:11:55,340 --> 00:11:56,860
<Default><b>Just one more time.</b></Default>

228
00:11:57,049 --> 00:11:58,329
<Default><b>One more try.</b></Default>

229
00:11:58,759 --> 00:11:59,839
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

230
00:12:16,570 --> 00:12:17,860
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

231
00:12:18,149 --> 00:12:22,159
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

232
00:12:22,490 --> 00:12:23,930
<Default><b>See, big brother?</b></Default>

233
00:12:24,039 --> 00:12:25,039
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

234
00:12:25,450 --> 00:12:26,460
<Default><b>Yeah!</b></Default>

235
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:28,940
<Default><b>You did it, Atla!</b></Default>

236
00:12:29,169 --> 00:12:30,529
<Default><b>[both laughing]</b></Default>

237
00:12:31,710 --> 00:12:33,015
<Default><b>You really did it!</b></Default>

238
00:12:33,039 --> 00:12:34,186
<Default><b>You stood up!</b></Default>

239
00:12:34,210 --> 00:12:35,370
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

240
00:12:35,629 --> 00:12:37,590
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

241
00:12:42,299 --> 00:12:43,759
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

242
00:12:48,269 --> 00:12:49,995
<Default><b>- [bell tolling]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

243
00:12:50,019 --> 00:12:51,166
<Default><b>[door crashes open]</b></Default>

244
00:12:51,190 --> 00:12:52,310
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

245
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:54,046
<Default><b>Wake up the
rest of the kids!</b></Default>

246
00:12:54,070 --> 00:12:55,990
<Default><b>- We're under attack!
- What?!</b></Default>

247
00:12:57,149 --> 00:12:58,429
<Default><b>[fire raging]</b></Default>

248
00:12:58,779 --> 00:13:00,360
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

249
00:13:01,909 --> 00:13:03,635
<Default><b>[SLAVER BOSS 03-A (M)]
Demi-humans from this village</b></Default>

250
00:13:03,659 --> 00:13:05,179
<Default><b>fetch a high price.</b></Default>

251
00:13:05,620 --> 00:13:07,000
<Default><b>Your orders...</b></Default>

252
00:13:07,330 --> 00:13:09,500
<Default><b>Are to take 'em alive!</b></Default>

253
00:13:10,419 --> 00:13:11,789
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

254
00:13:13,879 --> 00:13:16,145
<Default><b>[SLAVER 03-A (M)]
Throw down your swords, now!</b></Default>

255
00:13:16,169 --> 00:13:19,066
<Default><b>Unless you want something bad
to happen to your friend here!</b></Default>

256
00:13:19,090 --> 00:13:21,179
<Default><b>You coward!
Let go of her!</b></Default>

257
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:24,179
<Default><b>There's nothing cowardly
about using tactics.</b></Default>

258
00:13:24,389 --> 00:13:26,469
<Default><b>Now give up
and drop your weapons.</b></Default>

259
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,929
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

260
00:13:28,350 --> 00:13:29,600
<Default><b>Damn it!</b></Default>

261
00:13:31,769 --> 00:13:32,889
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

262
00:13:33,860 --> 00:13:35,956
<Default><b>[SLAVER 03-B (M)]
Search every house one by one!</b></Default>

263
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:37,660
<Default><b>[SLAVER 03-C (M)]
On it!</b></Default>

264
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:38,860
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

265
00:13:51,789 --> 00:13:53,029
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

266
00:13:53,460 --> 00:13:54,620
<Default><b>[laughter]</b></Default>

267
00:13:55,330 --> 00:13:57,105
<Default><b>If we sell all
of these brats</b></Default>

268
00:13:57,129 --> 00:13:59,395
<Default><b>we'll never have to work
another day in our lives!</b></Default>

269
00:13:59,419 --> 00:14:01,145
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN 03-A (F)]
Our homes are on fire!</b></Default>

270
00:14:01,169 --> 00:14:03,155
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN 03-B (F)] I wish
that Mom and Dad were here.</b></Default>

271
00:14:03,179 --> 00:14:04,799
<Default><b>Hey! Do it!</b></Default>

272
00:14:08,519 --> 00:14:09,679
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

273
00:14:12,269 --> 00:14:13,285
<Default><b>- [cracks]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

274
00:14:13,309 --> 00:14:14,349
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

275
00:14:18,529 --> 00:14:20,399
<Default><b>Our flag's
been destroyed.</b></Default>

276
00:14:21,190 --> 00:14:22,270
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

277
00:14:23,450 --> 00:14:24,490
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

278
00:14:25,110 --> 00:14:27,670
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I'm hiding a
signal flare back here.</b></Default>

279
00:14:28,029 --> 00:14:29,676
<Default><b>If you need to
call us for help</b></Default>

280
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:31,180
<Default><b>be sure to use it.</b></Default>

281
00:14:39,669 --> 00:14:40,749
<Default><b>[bursts]</b></Default>

282
00:14:45,129 --> 00:14:46,865
<Default><b>- [SLAVER 03-E (M)] Hey, kid!
- What?!</b></Default>

283
00:14:46,889 --> 00:14:48,649
<Default><b>What are you
doing there?</b></Default>

284
00:14:48,889 --> 00:14:50,720
<Default><b>- [thud]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

285
00:14:52,269 --> 00:14:53,269
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

286
00:14:53,690 --> 00:14:54,930
<Default><b>[FOHL] Atla!</b></Default>

287
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:57,206
<Default><b>Looks like you managed
to send up a signal</b></Default>

288
00:14:57,230 --> 00:14:58,546
<Default><b>calling for help, huh?</b></Default>

289
00:14:58,570 --> 00:15:00,336
<Default><b>Too bad by the
time it gets here</b></Default>

290
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,840
<Default><b>it'll be too late.</b></Default>

291
00:15:02,190 --> 00:15:05,110
<Default><b>Ah. A white
tiger? Lucky me.</b></Default>

292
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,716
<Default><b>Don't you
dare touch her!</b></Default>

293
00:15:06,740 --> 00:15:08,740
<Default><b>If you do, I'll
make you pay!</b></Default>

294
00:15:08,830 --> 00:15:09,910
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

295
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:12,240
<Default><b>Quit your squirming
and stay still!</b></Default>

296
00:15:13,039 --> 00:15:15,460
<Default><b>[screams]
You little brat!</b></Default>

297
00:15:15,539 --> 00:15:17,059
<Default><b>- [thuds]
- [shouts]</b></Default>

298
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:20,355
<Default><b>[SLAVER BOSS 03-A (M)] I don't
like the look in his eyes.</b></Default>

299
00:15:20,379 --> 00:15:22,235
<Default><b>And if we've got
this many slaves</b></Default>

300
00:15:22,259 --> 00:15:25,090
<Default><b>we're gonna need to use
this one here as an example.</b></Default>

301
00:15:31,850 --> 00:15:33,285
<Default><b>Big brother, run away!</b></Default>

302
00:15:33,309 --> 00:15:34,429
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

303
00:15:35,269 --> 00:15:36,850
<Default><b>Die, brat.</b></Default>

304
00:15:39,269 --> 00:15:40,309
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

305
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:42,190
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

306
00:15:42,570 --> 00:15:46,570
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

307
00:15:48,360 --> 00:15:50,080
<Default><b>The Shield Demon's here?</b></Default>

308
00:15:51,029 --> 00:15:53,080
<Default><b>Good job</b></Default>

309
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,880
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Shield Prison!</b></Default>

310
00:15:55,580 --> 00:15:56,700
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

311
00:16:01,250 --> 00:16:03,710
<Default><b>Damn!
How'd he get here so fast?</b></Default>

312
00:16:03,799 --> 00:16:06,129
<Default><b>You underestimated
how fast we can move.</b></Default>

313
00:16:06,379 --> 00:16:09,429
<Default><b>We're gonna make you regret
ever attacking this village!</b></Default>

314
00:16:13,389 --> 00:16:14,469
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

315
00:16:15,309 --> 00:16:16,509
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

316
00:16:17,139 --> 00:16:18,326
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

317
00:16:18,350 --> 00:16:19,430
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

318
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:24,570
<Default><b>Don't let a
single slaver escape!</b></Default>

319
00:16:24,779 --> 00:16:27,019
<Default><b>They burned all those houses
we built.</b></Default>

320
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:29,716
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Do you know how much
that will set us back?</b></Default>

321
00:16:29,740 --> 00:16:32,096
<Default><b>I don't give a damn
how much your houses cost.</b></Default>

322
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:34,159
<Default><b>Now die, Shield Demon!</b></Default>

323
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:35,700
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

324
00:16:36,409 --> 00:16:37,960
<Default><b>- [thuds]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

325
00:16:38,750 --> 00:16:40,080
<Default><b>Shield Prison!</b></Default>

326
00:16:40,669 --> 00:16:41,879
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

327
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,879
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

328
00:16:48,799 --> 00:16:50,235
<Default><b>[SLAVER BOSS]
What the hell is this?</b></Default>

329
00:16:50,259 --> 00:16:52,549
<Default><b>[banging]
Let me out! Let me out!</b></Default>

330
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:54,535
<Default><b>Be careful what
you wish for!</b></Default>

331
00:16:54,559 --> 00:16:55,889
<Default><b>Raphtalia!</b></Default>

332
00:16:58,269 --> 00:16:59,269
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

333
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:01,309
<Default><b>Brave Blade Mist!</b></Default>

334
00:17:08,069 --> 00:17:10,029
<Default><b>- [crashing]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

335
00:17:11,660 --> 00:17:12,755
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

336
00:17:12,779 --> 00:17:15,329
<Default><b>Stop, please!
I surrender!</b></Default>

337
00:17:15,529 --> 00:17:17,750
<Default><b>I surrender, all right?</b></Default>

338
00:17:18,710 --> 00:17:20,710
<Default><b>I've never
forgotten your face.</b></Default>

339
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:23,686
<Default><b>You're the one who kidnapped us
all those years ago.</b></Default>

340
00:17:23,710 --> 00:17:24,936
<Default><b>If you kill me</b></Default>

341
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:26,686
<Default><b>I promise you
that this village</b></Default>

342
00:17:26,710 --> 00:17:28,646
<Default><b>and everyone in
it will be done for!</b></Default>

343
00:17:28,670 --> 00:17:29,735
<Default><b>Shut up.</b></Default>

344
00:17:29,759 --> 00:17:32,130
<Default><b>Let those be
your last words</b></Default>

345
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:33,275
<Default><b>- [horse neighs]
Huh?</b></Default>

346
00:17:33,299 --> 00:17:35,140
<Default><b>[horses galloping]</b></Default>

347
00:17:36,970 --> 00:17:38,770
<Default><b>Sorry, I'm
late, everyone.</b></Default>

348
00:17:38,809 --> 00:17:40,730
<Default><b>No</b></Default>

349
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:43,809
<Default><b>We were just about to
execute this scum.</b></Default>

350
00:17:44,519 --> 00:17:45,519
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

351
00:17:45,609 --> 00:17:47,889
<Default><b>Guess you don't need
my help here then.</b></Default>

352
00:17:50,950 --> 00:17:52,319
<Default><b>This symbol.</b></Default>

353
00:17:52,569 --> 00:17:53,795
<Default><b>So then you're...</b></Default>

354
00:17:53,819 --> 00:17:55,019
<Default><b>[chuckling]</b></Default>

355
00:17:55,119 --> 00:17:56,639
<Default><b>Is something wrong?</b></Default>

356
00:17:57,490 --> 00:17:59,789
<Default><b>This symbol belongs
to a noble family</b></Default>

357
00:17:59,869 --> 00:18:01,805
<Default><b>from a region that
were devout worshipers</b></Default>

358
00:18:01,829 --> 00:18:03,829
<Default><b>- of the Three Heroes.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

359
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:05,305
<Default><b>Are you
trying to tell me</b></Default>

360
00:18:05,329 --> 00:18:07,106
<Default><b>that we can't
execute this guy</b></Default>

361
00:18:07,130 --> 00:18:09,370
<Default><b>because it might upset
a few noblemen?</b></Default>

362
00:18:09,460 --> 00:18:10,780
<Default><b>I'm afraid so.</b></Default>

363
00:18:12,880 --> 00:18:14,759
<Default><b>[grunts] [chuckles]</b></Default>

364
00:18:15,589 --> 00:18:18,140
<Default><b>We just have to make sure
he's alive, right?</b></Default>

365
00:18:18,349 --> 00:18:20,220
<Default><b>Yes, why do you ask?</b></Default>

366
00:18:20,390 --> 00:18:22,940
<Default><b>Each one of you
is going to become a slave.</b></Default>

367
00:18:23,099 --> 00:18:25,230
<Default><b>You intend to
sell me as a slave?</b></Default>

368
00:18:25,309 --> 00:18:26,956
<Default><b>You know that's
impossible, right?</b></Default>

369
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:27,900
<Default><b>You sure of that?</b></Default>

370
00:18:27,980 --> 00:18:30,005
<Default><b>You're gonna be
heading off to Siltvelt.</b></Default>

371
00:18:30,029 --> 00:18:31,990
<Default><b>[gasps] To Siltvelt?</b></Default>

372
00:18:32,069 --> 00:18:33,085
<Default><b>Y-You mean.</b></Default>

373
00:18:33,109 --> 00:18:35,505
<Default><b>The country that worships
the Shield Demon?</b></Default>

374
00:18:35,529 --> 00:18:37,966
<Default><b>And none other than the
"Shield Demon" himself</b></Default>

375
00:18:37,990 --> 00:18:40,070
<Default><b>is offering them
a gift of slaves.</b></Default>

376
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:42,579
<Default><b>With how well
they treat you over there</b></Default>

377
00:18:42,869 --> 00:18:46,000
<Default><b>you'll wish I had executed you
right here and now!</b></Default>

378
00:18:46,210 --> 00:18:48,210
<Default><b>No, please! I'll pay!</b></Default>

379
00:18:48,380 --> 00:18:50,186
<Default><b>Go and name
any price you like!</b></Default>

380
00:18:50,210 --> 00:18:51,696
<Default><b>Just don't make
me a slave!</b></Default>

381
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,815
<Default><b>Screw your money.</b></Default>

382
00:18:52,839 --> 00:18:54,606
<Default><b>I want you
to regret your actions</b></Default>

383
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:56,270
<Default><b>until the day you die!</b></Default>

384
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,800
<Default><b>[sobbing]</b></Default>

385
00:18:58,430 --> 00:18:59,825
<Default><b>Please show mercy!</b></Default>

386
00:18:59,849 --> 00:19:01,745
<Default><b>I'll do anything
but become someone's slave!</b></Default>

387
00:19:01,769 --> 00:19:02,825
<Default><b>Anything!</b></Default>

388
00:19:02,849 --> 00:19:04,825
<Default><b>I'll take back that I
called you a Demon!</b></Default>

389
00:19:04,849 --> 00:19:07,019
<Default><b>Please!</b></Default>

390
00:19:07,190 --> 00:19:10,126
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I explained things
to the Zeltoble slave merchant</b></Default>

391
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:12,750
<Default><b>and had him put all the
slavers up for auction.</b></Default>

392
00:19:14,109 --> 00:19:16,279
<Default><b>And while it was
a lot of extra work</b></Default>

393
00:19:16,660 --> 00:19:19,740
<Default><b>we managed to come out of it
with a decent amount of money.</b></Default>

394
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:22,789
<Default><b>I'm quite surprised
you did that to a noble.</b></Default>

395
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,976
<Default><b>Just make sure nobody tries to
get even with you, all right?</b></Default>

396
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:28,960
<Default><b>I made sure word got around
when I sold our wares.</b></Default>

397
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:32,130
<Default><b>Nobody will try to mess with
our village again.</b></Default>

398
00:19:33,049 --> 00:19:34,235
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
"The foolish humans</b></Default>"

399
00:19:34,259 --> 00:19:36,065
<Default><b>who attacked the
village of the Shield Hero</b></Default>

400
00:19:36,089 --> 00:19:37,866
<Default><b>who protects the
Demi-humans."</b></Default>

401
00:19:37,890 --> 00:19:39,650
<Default><b>When we
sold it like that</b></Default>

402
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,866
<Default><b>Siltvelt's nobles were
more than willing to</b></Default>

403
00:19:41,890 --> 00:19:43,690
<Default><b>pay a high
price for them.</b></Default>

404
00:19:45,890 --> 00:19:47,490
<Default><b>[ATLA] I can't sleep.</b></Default>

405
00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:50,420
<Default><b>Would you mind
if we talk for a bit, Master?</b></Default>

406
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:52,500
<Default><b>Well, just for a bit.</b></Default>

407
00:19:53,230 --> 00:19:54,910
<Default><b>It's been bothering me.</b></Default>

408
00:19:55,109 --> 00:19:58,189
<Default><b>I couldn't do anything when
the village was being attacked.</b></Default>

409
00:19:58,910 --> 00:20:00,255
<Default><b>I'm afraid I've
always been</b></Default>

410
00:20:00,279 --> 00:20:02,399
<Default><b>nothing but a burden
to my brother.</b></Default>

411
00:20:03,079 --> 00:20:05,879
<Default><b>I don't want to spend
the rest of my life like this.</b></Default>

412
00:20:06,539 --> 00:20:08,459
<Default><b>I want to be
strong like you.</b></Default>

413
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,600
<Default><b>Don't worry about that.</b></Default>

414
00:20:10,670 --> 00:20:12,065
<Default><b>When I'm all finished</b></Default>

415
00:20:12,089 --> 00:20:14,799
<Default><b>everyone here will be able
to protect themselves.</b></Default>

416
00:20:15,130 --> 00:20:17,259
<Default><b>Great. Once I'm strong</b></Default>

417
00:20:17,930 --> 00:20:19,130
<Default><b>I'll try...</b></Default>

418
00:20:19,390 --> 00:20:21,430
<Default><b>To be a shield
that protects you.</b></Default>

419
00:20:21,759 --> 00:20:23,279
<Default><b>That's what I want.</b></Default>

420
00:20:23,349 --> 00:20:24,509
<Default><b>Is it now?</b></Default>

421
00:20:26,559 --> 00:20:27,559
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

422
00:20:31,769 --> 00:20:33,169
<Default><b>[slight chuckle]</b></Default>

423
00:20:35,650 --> 00:20:37,770
<Default><b>You gotta watch her
more carefully.</b></Default>

424
00:20:37,819 --> 00:20:39,579
<Default><b>She wound
up at my place.</b></Default>

425
00:20:39,700 --> 00:20:41,200
<Default><b>- I'm not...
- Hm?</b></Default>

426
00:20:42,279 --> 00:20:44,910
<Default><b>I'm not strong enough
to protect Atla.</b></Default>

427
00:20:45,450 --> 00:20:47,170
<Default><b>But I really want to be!</b></Default>

428
00:20:49,619 --> 00:20:51,396
<Default><b>You're
siblings, all right.</b></Default>

429
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:52,815
<Default><b>You know,
tomorrow morning</b></Default>

430
00:20:52,839 --> 00:20:54,896
<Default><b>I'm going to be
resetting Sadeena's level.</b></Default>

431
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:56,320
<Default><b>You should join.</b></Default>

432
00:20:56,380 --> 00:20:57,380
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

433
00:20:58,420 --> 00:21:00,485
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I reset
Sadeena and Fohl's levels</b></Default>

434
00:21:00,509 --> 00:21:03,469
<Default><b>so that they could take full
advantage of my hero buffs.</b></Default>

435
00:21:04,390 --> 00:21:07,430
<Default><b>I'm expecting a lot from them
when it comes time to fight.</b></Default>

436
00:21:07,769 --> 00:21:09,616
<Default><b>I need to start getting
everyone ready</b></Default>

437
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:12,080
<Default><b>for the inevitable battle
with the Phoenix.</b></Default>

438
00:21:22,450 --> 00:21:23,740
<Default><b>Shield Hero!</b></Default>

439
00:21:28,119 --> 00:21:29,539
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

440
00:21:34,539 --> 00:21:35,979
<Default><b>[FOHL] Excuse me.</b></Default>

441
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:37,890
<Default><b>What's wrong, brother?</b></Default>

442
00:21:38,420 --> 00:21:39,589
<Default><b>Her eyes.</b></Default>

443
00:21:40,420 --> 00:21:42,900
<Default><b>[FOHL] Do you need something
from my sister?</b></Default>

444
00:21:43,470 --> 00:21:44,550
<Default><b>No, I...</b></Default>

445
00:21:44,849 --> 00:21:46,529
<Default><b>What is your name, boy?</b></Default>

446
00:21:46,890 --> 00:21:48,010
<Default><b>I'm Fohl.</b></Default>

447
00:21:48,390 --> 00:21:49,980
<Default><b>And my name is Atla.</b></Default>

448
00:21:51,019 --> 00:21:52,190
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

449
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:54,639
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

450
00:22:00,650 --> 00:22:02,130
<Default><b>That man just now.</b></Default>

451
00:22:02,359 --> 00:22:04,240
<Default><b>He felt so much like you</b></Default>

452
00:22:04,319 --> 00:22:06,679
<Default><b>I thought you were in
two places at once.</b></Default>

453
00:22:07,619 --> 00:22:08,619
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

454
00:22:08,700 --> 00:22:12,710
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

455
00:22:13,829 --> 00:22:15,149
<Default><b>[sharp exhale]</b></Default>

456
00:22:15,210 --> 00:22:16,610
<Default><b>[MIRELIA] I see.</b></Default>

457
00:22:16,710 --> 00:22:18,420
<Default><b>So that's what he said.</b></Default>

458
00:22:19,130 --> 00:22:22,180
<Default><b>Young lady</b></Default>

459
00:22:32,059 --> 00:22:35,440
<Default><b>Do you know the stories
of the Staff Hero's heroics?</b></Default>

460
00:22:35,730 --> 00:22:38,359
<Default><b>What? There are stories
about that loser?</b></Default>

461
00:22:38,730 --> 00:22:42,200
<Default><b>His name then was</b></Default>

462
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:44,886
<Default><b>[MIRELIA] He abandoned
his nation and name</b></Default>

463
00:22:44,910 --> 00:22:47,579
<Default><b>to become an ordinary soldier
of Melromarc</b></Default>

464
00:22:47,869 --> 00:22:50,410
<Default><b>going on to achieve
fame and glory.</b></Default>

465
00:22:52,250 --> 00:22:54,250
<Default><b>He used his
strategic talent</b></Default>

466
00:22:54,329 --> 00:22:55,646
<Default><b>and immense intellect</b></Default>

467
00:22:55,670 --> 00:22:58,190
<Default><b>whenever he could
for the sake of his sister.</b></Default>

468
00:22:58,630 --> 00:23:01,549
<Default><b>Time and time again</b></Default>

469
00:23:03,009 --> 00:23:05,180
<Default><b>One day</b></Default>

470
00:23:05,259 --> 00:23:07,059
<Default><b>by the nation
of Siltvelt.</b></Default>

471
00:23:07,890 --> 00:23:10,140
<Default><b>Upon learning
this horrid news</b></Default>

472
00:23:10,269 --> 00:23:12,069
<Default><b>he was driven
to vengeance</b></Default>

473
00:23:12,099 --> 00:23:13,379
<Default><b>and in a fury</b></Default>

474
00:23:13,519 --> 00:23:16,230
<Default><b>he defeated their king</b></Default>

475
00:23:16,900 --> 00:23:17,940
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

476
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,800
<Default><b>[slight chuckle]</b></Default>

477
00:23:19,900 --> 00:23:22,240
<Default><b>But I didn't call you here
for stories.</b></Default>

478
00:23:22,609 --> 00:23:23,609
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

479
00:23:23,690 --> 00:23:25,676
<Default><b>Why is it that
you called us here?</b></Default>

480
00:23:25,700 --> 00:23:27,980
<Default><b>Is there something
you have to tell us?</b></Default>

481
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:30,329
<Default><b>Yes. We've located him.</b></Default>

482
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:32,750
<Default><b>The Spear
Hero, Motoyasu.</b></Default>

